rrang!_Awards_winners&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Category:Kerrang! Awards winners (page does not exist)">Kerrang! Awards winners</a></li><li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Category:Musical_groups_established_in_1983&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Category:Musical groups established in 1983 (page does not exist)">Musical groups established in 1983</a></li><li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Category:Musical_groups_from_Los_Angeles,_California&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Category:Musical groups from Los Angeles, California (page does not exist)">Musical groups from Los Angeles, California</a></li><li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Category:Musical_quartets&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Category:Musical quartets (page does not exist)">Musical quartets</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Rock_and_Roll_Hall_of_Fame_inductees" title="Category:Rock and Roll Hall of Fame inductees">Rock and Roll Hall of Fame inductees</a></li><li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Category:Warner_Bros._Records_artists&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Category:Warner Bros. Records artists (page does not exist)">Warner Bros. Records artists</a></li><li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Category:1983_establishments_in_California&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Category:1983 establishments in California (page does not exist)">1983 establishments in California</a></li></ul></div></div>												<div class="visualClear"></div>
